title: Week 7 Waivers 2022
description:
Field Yates, Liz Loza and Daniel Dopp recap MNF including another bad performance from Russ, talk who can be a Top 20 performer for the rest of the season and what players’ stock is on the rise. Plus, Eric Moody joins to tell us who to target on the waiver wire.
